'''''The Battle of Ahto: A Memoir''''' was the memoir of [[Order of Shasa|Shasan adept]] [[Fewash Welko]]. Part of the book recounted the [[Battle of Ahto]] and his meeting with [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] afterward. The book was originally written in [[Selkath (language)|Selkatha]], and was later translated into [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].

